data.description: Welcome to this one story home, privately set on 1.22 acres. Step into the oversized living room with wood burning fireplace and natural brick surround. All appliances remain in the kitchen with plenty of countertop space. Family Room and dining room each located off of the kitchen, along with sliding glass door leading to back deck and backyard. Primary en-suite with stand-up shower & ample closet space. Mudroom & laundry room off of 2 -car garage with tandem shop area. Newer furnace with Air-Conditioning! Enjoy this private setting and make it your own!
